From c669fddae0b3eea17a99cf6df8b5b170b0aee668 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Adyel Ullahil Mamun <adyel.ullahil@therapservices.net>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 12:16:54 +0600
Subject: [PATCH] fix: add cookie-based session auth for GET attendance
 verification

- Add second login via /auth/api/v1/login to establish session cookies
  (the /api/v1/attendances/ endpoint requires cookie auth, not Bearer token)
- Include maxInactiveMinutes and cookieEnabled params in login request
- Remove experimental Provider-Code/X-Provider headers from GET request
- Add detailed debug logging: full URL, request/response headers,
  session cookies, and response body for easier troubleshooting
- Add 60s timeout on GET verification request
---
 attendance_data.xlsx | Bin 8647 -> 8662 bytes
 test_attendance.js   |  79 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-----------
 2 files changed, 60 insertions(+), 19 deletions(-)

